Enid dear you should see my stump baby in its latest stage! i am sending it to Amama tomorrow or the day after, by insured Express - I surely know that my Mommie will do all that is possible for me, and you know how much "it" means to me! Please tell Amamma to tell me jsut how it impresses her and also you and Ottocar. - We have several of the books on your last list and will send them as soon as Daddy gets through with them. Did you get the ones we sent? There must have been 5 or six sent at different times, you do not mention receiving any, I mean Amamma 
How about the Artists League? 
Enid why don't you find out how to get into the "Daughters of the American Revolution I don't think it woudl cost much - and you would need 

