Sig and Maxine are mvoing into their little home - How I would like to buy it for them! Only $350.00 in the price! They are renting it and Sigurd with the help of Bill Macmullen did all the cleaning and placing of the furniture and even the making of the cutest curt-ains you ever saw! It was a surprise for Max! 
