ooms from tip to too - I do hope they will not freeze!! Alice took old carpets and gummy socks and papers and covered her little garden with them - the rows were all up so slick and so straight we have a lovely new pool about twice as wide as the one you know, and if any one wants to give me anything ever, I do hope it will be water lillies, hardy ones! We have about 16 fan sails now - they are so pretty! 
